Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也很早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有田径部的晨练
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这只猫该怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可能的话想收养它 不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问问秋子阿姨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只需一秒就会有答复的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的只需要一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是注意不要让它靠近名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那孩子对猫过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定收养了 那接下来就要给它取个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮它起个可爱的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一来起么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样 我可是对女孩子的喜好了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫塚茂夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人名一样听了就不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰塚泰夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想个更可爱一点的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…不行么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就叫“肉包子”如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是喜欢肉包子么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算喜欢也不要用食物的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 皮洛西基
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以叫它“小皮洛” 听起来很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱是可爱 但那词是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有特别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯粹是来源于我心中那诱惑少女心的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名字也是从少女小宇宙中所诞生出的词汇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 虽然不理解你说的 但是很可爱 就用这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始你就是皮洛了 好么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮洛 皮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PIROZHKI不是俄国的油炸包子么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正真琴也很喜欢 不是挺好么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮洛 皮洛 皮洛 皮洛皮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要带着它去托儿所么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想跟它在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真说得出来 明明曾把它从天桥抛下过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 真琴总感觉自己在失去记忆之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被这孩子救起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下钱包什么的然后独自离开之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事可能会有么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情好的时候就把它当成是自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然它自己粘上真琴 那它就是真琴的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 皮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么肉包子会那么好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在问些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常对话而已 日常对话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是日常对话那也是很难回答的话题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我通过研究肉包子的制作过程 再告诉你为何如此美味的秘密么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要说句“真好吃”之类的敷衍一下不就行了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不恶心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 别跑 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}第8话\N追忆的幻想曲\N～fantasia～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你我才能找到真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所说 她去了眺望之丘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道她在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的对于真琴一点都不了解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是感觉在那里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是感觉到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙不知道自己是谁 失去记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是知道什么的话告诉我吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的话说不定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么冷的天 那个家伙在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是你的熟人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧 虽然笨手笨脚的还很怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫真琴 泽渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的名字是真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 在等我么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是不坦率呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个… 我把皮洛带去托儿所结果被训了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是明天不许再带过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我买肉包子给你 打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你一开始也是这么打算的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你又怎么会来等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 就是这么打算的 对吧 皮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你起码要先敲门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一你自己不也是不敲门就进真琴的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了你快出去 我正在补被你剪掉的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜 你再这么说我就不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得想给你看样好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的裸体的话已经看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是真琴的裸体！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看不到那么可爱的东西的祐一真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好东西是指这个么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做作业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 不好了 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮洛又在吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披洛好像吃坏肚子了很痛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算弄干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不能去舞那边了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好对待那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喝了冷牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要光是嘴上说可爱 要更小心点照顾它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮洛 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去确实认识一个叫这个名字的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个人不是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴 是我小时候喜欢的年长女性的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 知道这个名字的人应该没有才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了那时候在我房间里的那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可能么 我到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子应该不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 恢复健康了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得脚下很虚 大概是因为昨天没睡好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你是一年级的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以问下你的名字么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野 天野见汐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相泽祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 昨天的那个女孩子还记得么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做她的朋友么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她因为某些原因所以认识的人很少 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有记忆对么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么想要我做她的朋友呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也比较难说明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是认为你的话说不定会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做那女孩的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么残酷的事情怎么有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会成为那女孩的朋友 绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你和舞都只会说这些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底你们知道真琴些什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你们都知道些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是过去认识的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是说曾经遇见过她的人 那是相泽你本人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？和她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定曾经见过 在很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那个时候她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线索？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我又想起一个线索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于自己过去的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我曾经在这里待过很久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里有什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我和那个家伙分手的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛突然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道理由 但就是感觉非常生气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉在这里曾发生过非常讨厌的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 在这个地方么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点下山吧 在天气变冷之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会买肉包子给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天当然会冷 天热到出汗的话就是异常天气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常对话而已 日常对话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概又要下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的话当然会下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“要是下海胆和栗子的话那就可怕了”对么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真清楚呢 我想要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然知道了 祐一的想法太容易猜透了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起连我都变成傻瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你意思是真琴是傻瓜所以祐一也受感染了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是两个人一起变傻瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“啊 原来如此” 咦 我应该赞同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可是很珍贵的哦 能够作为笨蛋的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 开始下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心跟皮洛一样吃坏肚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 那可以让祐一照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会照顾你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 会摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪 下雪 下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙也渐渐变得率直了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一还真是悠闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈正在找她的父母呢 还去了警察局和市役所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却找不着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连寻人启事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子应该是有家人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮洛 皮洛 皮洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一下子就兴奋成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 不是跟你说了进来要敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起做纸飞机吧 纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 你又打算蹂躏我的作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有一个人做 但总是折不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那管我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起做吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然闯进来有意见 先敲门也有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太蛮横了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就没些折中的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要从一个极端到另一个极端
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说这个了 你看 我买了新的漫画 一起看么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起看漫画有什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边说这里有趣边一起看很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你很空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很空 但是不喜欢你的说话方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 祐一 这个很有趣 一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个字不会念 怎么念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这个字都不会念么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么祐一帮我念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离太远就看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 恋爱总是那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是纠缠不清的少女漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要插些无关紧要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹泻也总是那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种书上根本没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 再从头开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱总是那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 一定会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到那时 两人就再也不分开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前…再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜 真是感人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后也是纠缠不清的结尾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人正在回味的时候可以不要泼冷水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方就证明你还是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓“结婚是人生的墓场”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟祐一结婚的人太悲惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会跟你结婚的所以放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟你的话我肯定咬舌自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始第三次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么手总是不听使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么给你勺子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不了的话没办法呢 我会连你的那份一起吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我 那是真琴的 还给我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮洛在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候钻进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 皮洛 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它正睡着就不要动它了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的 你也回房睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 真琴也要和皮洛一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就忍那么一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么真琴也在这里睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮洛 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那我去你房间睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 想要一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想要永远在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是在梦境中 漫长的梦境中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前 这样跟我睡在一起的那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人的名字叫真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫作泽渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收治了在山上受伤的那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后瞒着所有人 在这里一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想对我复仇么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么最近没有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也好 就算是你不恶作剧的时候也是满可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后因为口无遮拦所以不要说话 态度再慎重点 穿着可爱点 脸稍微改变下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是全要变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别生气 作为赔礼 从今以后叫你真琴星人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这听了让我更生气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴不是人类对么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾有个这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也曾经历过相同的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子只是来见相泽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外应该没有别的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事 那家伙的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想见你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个她化为人类从山上下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在相泽同学正处于转瞬即失的奇迹之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这奇迹只是一瞬的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子用自己的生命交换来的 仅有的一点光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用生命交换的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换来奇迹需要作出两个牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆 还有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是说 难道她的生命马上就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是体力会逐渐衰弱 变的越来越难以像正常人一般活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院和医生都没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什么都不知道么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己马上就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到来的分离将会随着相泽同学对她的用情越深而愈加的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你先做好这个觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 请不要再让我卷进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你能联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是不喜欢住在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能更关心她一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的东西就行了么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天来了 如果一直都是春天多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.45,0:24:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,0)\an8\fs26}第9话\N小狐狸的摇篮曲\N～berceuse～
